</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>fileNames</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The list of file and/or folder path(s) to be added. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cloudConnection</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The cloud connection used to fetch file data. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>checkSumCheck</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Whether to validate files by comparing checksums with the server. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
